SUBLIME TEXT DARK SIDEBAR

How to install:

1. Open Sublime Text 2 and go to Preferences -> Browse Packages.
2. Locate the Theme - Default folder.
3. Open the Files folder and copy its content to the Theme - Default folder.
4. In ST2 go to Preferences -> Setting - User and paste the following line of code:
     "theme": "Dark.sublime-theme"
5. Restart ST2 and you're done.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Como instalar:

1. Inicia Sublime Text 2 y ve al menú Preferences -> Browse Packages.
2. Localiza la carpeta Theme - Default.
3. Abre l carpeta Files y copia su contenido en Theme - Default.
4. En ST2 ve a Preferences -> Setting - User y pega la siguiente línea de código:
     "theme": "Dark.sublime-theme"
5. Reinicia ST2 y listo.